### ============================================================
### Mall Cloud — Product 模块接口测试脚本
### 直连商品服务端口（不经过 Gateway / BFF）
###
### 使用方式：IDEA 打开 → 点绿色箭头逐个运行
###
### Step 1：testLogin → 获取 Token
### Step 2+：后续请求自动携带 Token
### ============================================================

@ADMIN = http://localhost:8030
@PRODUCT = http://localhost:8023


### ============================================================
### Step 1：获取 Token（testLogin 跳过验证码）
### ============================================================

# @name testLogin
POST {{ADMIN}}/v1/auth/user/testLogin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}


### ============================================================
### Step 2：商品中心（B端，需 token）
### ============================================================

### 2.1 商品分页
# @name searchProduct
POST {{PRODUCT}}/v1/product/searchByPage
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10}

### 2.2 ES商品搜索
# @name searchFromES
POST {{PRODUCT}}/v1/product/searchFromES
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10}

### 2.3 商品详情
# @name findProduct
GET {{PRODUCT}}/v1/product/findById?id=1825358818617536512
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

### 2.4 新增商品
# @name insertProduct
POST {{PRODUCT}}/v1/product/insert
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"name":"测试商品","price":99,"categoryId":1,"brandId":1,"unitId":1}

### 2.5 修改商品
# @name updateProduct
POST {{PRODUCT}}/v1/product/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"id":1,"name":"修改后名称"}

### 2.6 删除商品
# @name deleteProduct
POST {{PRODUCT}}/v1/product/deleteByIds
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

[1]


